https://play.tailwindcss.com/BX3obIMkBV

**Describe your issue**

I am using the `@utility` function to define things such as button styles. Here I define base styles, and then variant styles such as Solid/Outline.

It looks something like this:
```css
@utility button {
  @apply button--solid; /* Use button solid as base style */
}

@utility button--solid {}
@utility button--outline {}
```

My issue is that the `@variant x` from `button--solid` is not imported into `button`, as I would expect.

